  "prompt": "How can I reach Pune from Mumbai?",
  "response": "There are several ways to travel from Mumbai to Pune:\n\n1. By Road:\n- Private bus\n- State transport bus (MSRTC)\n- Private car/taxi\n- Distance is approximately 150 km\n- Travel time is around 3-4 hours depending on traffic\n\n2. By Train:\n- Multiple trains connect Mumbai and Pune\n- Options include Deccan Express, Indrayani Express\n- Travel time is around 3-3.5 hours\n- Departs from Mumbai CST or Dadar stations\n\n3. By Flight:\n- Direct flights from Mumbai to Pune\n- Short flight duration (about 45 minutes)\n- Operated by airlines like IndiGo, Air India\n- Departs from Mumbai domestic airport\n\n4. Shared Cab/Taxi:\n- Prepaid taxi services\n- Private cab services\n- Shared taxi options available\n\n5. Self-Drive:\n- Via Mumbai-Pune Expressway\n- Fastest and most convenient route\n- Scenic drive takes around 2.5-3 hours\n\nChoose the mode of transport based on your budget, time, and convenience.",
